Title: When adding views to reports the currently selected filters are now honored
Level: 2
Edition: cee
Component: reporting
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.7i4
Date: 1454956397
Class: fix

This means that if you have modified some filters in a view and add that view
to a report these filters are now being saved in the report as well. So the
view in the report has exactly the same object selection.
